title: [Gyldemar Forest, Ancient Road]
description: Dark bricks form the road to the north and south.  Tufts of dry grass sprout from cracks in the mortar between stones.  A small tree has pushed its way up through the bricks like a volcano forming from a plain.

Dark bricks form the road to the north and south.  Tufts of dry grass sprout from cracks in the mortar between stones.  A small tree has pushed its way up through the bricks like a volcano forming from a plain.  The cool night air whistles through the tree.
